---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <main class="mx-auto md:mx-[10.5rem] min-h-screen font-work">

        <h1 class="font-bebas text-4xl text-center mt-20 mb-10">
            Economic Indicators</h1>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">

            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-3 mr-2">
                <a href="/eco_footprint">
                    <div class="relative w-full h-40">
                        <img src="/img/foto/ecological_footprint_detail.png" alt="ecological footprint chart detail"
                            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-3 px-1">
                        <h1
                            class="font-literata text-lg uppercase text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 tracking-wide font-semibold mb-1">
                            Ecological Footprint</h1>
                        <p>
                            Just two countries have high human development and a sustainable lifestyle.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </a>


            </div>


            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-3 mr-2">
                <a href="/happy_and_sustainable">
                    <div class="relative w-full h-40"> <!-- Consistent height -->
                        <img src="/img/foto/happy&sustainable_detail.png" alt=""
                            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-coverr">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-3 px-1">
                        <h1
                            class="font-literata text-lg uppercase text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 tracking-wide font-semibold mb-1">
                            Happy & Sustainable</h1>
                        <p>
                            Happiness score, emissions and more in one big bubble chart.
                        </p>

                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>

        </div>

        <h1 class="font-bebas text-4xl text-center mt-20 mb-10">Model Gallery</h1>


        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1 text-pretty">
                <a href="/model_gallery/toc_graph">
                    <h1
                        class="font-literata text-lg uppercase text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 tracking-wide font-semibold mb-1">
                        TOC Graph</h1>
                    <p>A graph view of the model gallery series. Models, theories and systems and their connections.</p>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1 text-pretty">
                <a href="/model_gallery/schelling_segregation">
                    <h1
                        class="font-literata text-lg uppercase text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 tracking-wide font-semibold mb-1">
                        Schelling's Segregation</h1>
                    <p>Simulation of individual decisons leading to emergend segregation.</p>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1 text-pretty">
                <a href="/model_gallery/linear_regression">
                    <h1
                        class="font-literata text-lg uppercase text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 tracking-wide font-semibold mb-1">
                        Linear Regression</h1>
                    <p>A short introduction to the fundamental model.</p>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1 text-pretty">
                <a href="/model_gallery/confusion_matrix">
                    <h1
                        class="font-literata text-lg uppercase text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 tracking-wide font-semibold mb-1">
                        Confusion Matrix</h1>
                    <p>Fill in your false and true positives/negatives and see accuracy, precision, recall and more.</p>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1 text-pretty">
                <a href="/model_gallery/logistic_growth">
                    <h1
                        class="font-literata text-lg uppercase text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 tracking-wide font-semibold mb-1">
                        Logistic Growth</h1>
                    <p>Inspired by Thomas Malthus model of population growth. Also known as sigmoid curve in statistics.
                    </p>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1 text-pretty">
                <a href="/model_gallery/logistic_map">
                    <h1
                        class="font-literata text-lg uppercase text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 tracking-wide font-semibold mb-1">
                        Logistic Map</h1>
                    <p class="text-wrap">A simple modulation of the logistic growth model that produces phenomena like
                        convergence or chaotic oscillations.</p>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1 text-pretty">
                <a href="/model_gallery/normal_distribution">
                    <h1
                        class="font-literata text-lg uppercase text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 tracking-wide font-semibold mb-1">
                        Normal Distribution</h1>
                    <p class="text-wrap">Natures preferred distribution.</p>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1 text-pretty">
                <a href="/model_gallery/demand_and_supply">
                    <h1
                        class="font-literata text-lg uppercase text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 tracking-wide font-semibold mb-1">
                        Supply and Demand</h1>
                    <p class="text-wrap">The cornerstone model of neoclassical economics.</p>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1 text-pretty">
                <a href="/model_gallery/corn_model">
                    <h1
                        class="font-literata text-lg uppercase text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 tracking-wide font-semibold mb-1">
                        Corn Model</h1>
                    <p class="text-wrap">Ricardo's three-factor economy.</p>
                </a>
            </div>



        </div>


    </main>
</Layout>